OL,3,CLike 'diving off a skyscraper
OL,4,Cbackwards': Artemis II crew describe
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,FWatch the best moments from the
OL,8,FArtemis II mission news conference
OL,10,FThe Artemis II astronauts have
OL,11,Fdescribed their historic mission
OL,12,Faround the moon in their first press
OL,13,Fconference, saying their time in free
OL,14,Ffall felt like "if you dove off ... a
OL,15,Fskyscraper backwards".
OL,17,F"That's what it felt like for five
OL,18,Fseconds," Victor Glover said on
OL,19,FThursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
