OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776423774
OL,3,CLike 'diving off a skyscraper
OL,4,Cbackwards': Artemis II crew describe
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,FThe crew arrived safely back on Earth
OL,8,Flast week after their 10-day trip,
OL,9,Fmarking the first time astronauts have
OL,10,Fbeen to the moon since the final
OL,11,FApollo flight in 1972.
OL,13,FThey travelled deeper into space than
OL,14,Fany humans before them, surpassing the
OL,15,FApollo 13 record from 1970, when they
OL,16,Freached 252,756 miles (406,771
OL,17,Fkilometres) away from Earth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
