OL,3,CLike 'diving off a skyscraper
OL,4,Cbackwards': Artemis II crew describe
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FDuring reentry, their capsule was
OL,13,Ftravelling more than 30 times the
OL,14,Fspeed of sound.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
