OL,3,CLike 'diving off a skyscraper
OL,4,Cbackwards': Artemis II crew describe
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,FGlover described it as a visceral
OL,8,Fexperience, saying he was stunned by
OL,9,Fthe sound of parachutes deploying
OL,10,Fafter the Orion capsule plummeted
OL,11,Fthrough the air and experienced a six-
OL,12,Fminute communications blackout due to
OL,13,Fplasma created by the sheer speed at
OL,14,Fwhich their vehicle was moving.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
