OL,3,CLike 'diving off a skyscraper
OL,4,Cbackwards': Artemis II crew describe
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,F"When we came home, we were shocked at
OL,8,Fthe global outpouring of support, of
OL,9,Fpride, of ownership of this mission,"
OL,10,FReid Wiseman said during the
OL,11,Finterview. "That's what the four of us
OL,12,Fwanted. We wanted to go out and try to
OL,13,Fdo something that would bring the
OL,14,Fworld together."
OL,16,FChristina Koch said it was difficult
OL,17,Fto describe how much it meant to them
OL,18,Fto hear that the mission had such a
OL,19,Fbig impact on those watching from
OL,20,FEarth.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@eO]sD@LOUvD@PO]
