OL,3,CLike 'diving off a skyscraper
OL,4,Cbackwards': Artemis II crew describe
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,F"I cannot overstate how important that
OL,8,Fwas to us," she said. "It was every
OL,9,Fbit as important as accomplishing the
OL,10,Ftechnical goals and being there for
OL,11,Four NASA teammates was to make this
OL,12,Fthe world's mission."
OL,14,FReid Wiseman, Victor Glover, Christina
OL,15,FKoch and Jeremy Hansen launched to the
OL,16,Fmoon from Florida on April 1.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@KO]pD@WOUtD@UO]
