OL,3,CLike 'diving off a skyscraper
OL,4,Cbackwards': Artemis II crew describe
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,FNASA is already working on Artemis
OL,8,FIII, the next step in its grand moon
OL,9,Fbase-building plans. The platform from
OL,10,Fwhich the rocket launches headed back
OL,11,Fon Thursday to Kennedy Space Centre's
OL,12,FVehicle Assembly Building, where it
OL,13,Fwill be prepped for next year's launch.
OL,15,FStill awaiting an assigned crew,
OL,16,FArtemis III will remain in orbit
OL,17,Faround Earth as astronauts practice
OL,18,Fdocking their Orion capsule with one
OL,19,For two lunar landers in development by
OL,20,FElon Musk's SpaceX and Jeff Bezos'
OL,21,FBlue Origin.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
